{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"automation","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:8BrazeKit0A0C13ConfigurationC4PushC10AutomationC","text":"Automation","identifier":"doc:\/\/Braze\/documentation\/BrazeKit\/Braze\/Configuration-swift.class\/Push-swift.class\/Automation-swift.class","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The SDK must be initialized on the main thread to enable push notification"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"automation. SDK initialization must happen before the application has finished launching"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or in your AppDelegate ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/archive.is\/nUG1k"},{"text":" implementation.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If the application setup requires the SDK to be initialized after the application has","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"finished launching, refer to the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Braze\/documentation\/BrazeKit\/Braze\/prepareForDelayedInitialization(pushAutomation:)","isActive":true},{"text":" method.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Important","type":"aside","style":"important"},{"name":"Note","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The automation steps performed by the SDK are compatible with pre-existing push"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"notification handling integrations in your codebase. The SDK only automates the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"processing of remote notification received from Braze. Any system handler implemented","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to process your own or another third party SDK remote notifications will continue to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"work when ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"automation"},{"type":"text","text":" is enabled."}]}],"type":"aside"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, the SDK does not perform any automation steps and you are required to implement"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIApplicationDelegate"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" methods yourself as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"described in the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Braze\/tutorials\/Braze\/b1-standard-push-notifications","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" tutorial."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can enable automatic push notification handling as follows:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["configuration.push.automation = true"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This instructs the SDK to:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register your application for push notification on the system."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Request the push notification authorization \/ permission at initialization.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Dynamically provide implementations for the push notification related system delegate"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"methods.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For a more granular behavior, each automation step can be enabled individually:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Automate only the `application(_:didRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithDeviceToken:)`","\/\/ delegate method","configuration.push.automation.registerDeviceToken = true"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Or you can perform a combination of both approaches:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Enable all automations","configuration.push.automation = true","\/\/ Disable the automatic notification authorization request at launch.","configuration.push.automation.requestAuthorizationAtLaunch = false"],"syntax":null},{"name":"Important","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When enabled, the "},{"code":"UIApplicationDelegate","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" methods will not be executed when processing remote"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"notifications received from Braze."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Use ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BrazeKit\/Braze\/Notifications-swift.class\/subscribeToUpdates(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" to subscribe to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"those push notification updates when ","type":"text"},{"code":"automation","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is enabled."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"important"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The behavior of each automation step is described in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Braze\/documentation\/BrazeKit\/Braze\/Configuration-swift.class\/Push-swift.class\/Automation-swift.class","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:8BrazeKit0A0C13ConfigurationC4PushC10automationAG10AutomationCvp","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"text":" ","kind":"tex